  description: "Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh ven bi\u1EC3n thu\u1ED9c
    v\xF9ng Duy\xEAn h\u1EA3i Nam Trung B\u1ED9 c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam. Trung t\xE2m
    c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Nha Trang, m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng
    \u0111i\u1EC3m du l\u1ECBch bi\u1EC3n n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng c\u1EE7a c\u1EA3 n\u01B0\u1EDBc.
    Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u danh lam th\u1EAFng c\u1EA3nh h\u1EA5p d\u1EABn
    nh\u01B0 V\u1ECBnh Nha Trang, Th\xE1p B\xE0 Ponagar v\xE0 V\u1ECBnh V\xE2n Phong.\n\nT\u1EC9nh
    n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n bi\u1EC3n v\xE0
    m\xF3n \u0103n \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng nh\u01B0 Y\u1EBFn s\xE0o Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a,
    B\xFAn s\u1EE9a Nha Trang v\xE0 Nem n\u01B0\u1EDBng Nha Trang.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n
    h\xF3a, Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a ch\u1ECBu \u1EA3nh h\u01B0\u1EDFng c\u1EE7a v\u0103n
    h\xF3a Ch\u0103m c\u1ED5, th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n r\xF5 qua c\xE1c di t\xEDch nh\u01B0
    Th\xE1p B\xE0 Ponagar v\xE0 nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng.
    M\u1ED9t l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i ti\xEAu bi\u1EC3u l\xE0 L\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i Th\xE1p B\xE0
    Ponagar, thu h\xFAt \u0111\xF4ng \u0111\u1EA3o ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xE2n v\xE0 du
    kh\xE1ch \u0111\u1EBFn tham gia, ph\u1EA3n \xE1nh t\xEDn ng\u01B0\u1EE1ng v\xE0
    \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a c\u01B0
    d\xE2n v\xF9ng bi\u1EC3n mi\u1EC1n Trung."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1/7/2025, t\u1EC9nh Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a v\xE0 Ninh Thu\u1EADn
    h\u1EE3p nh\u1EA5t th\xE0nh t\u1EC9nh Kh\xE1nh H\xF2a m\u1EDBi, tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh
    c\u1EF1c t\u0103ng tr\u01B0\u1EDFng m\u1EA1nh m\u1EBD v\u1EDBi di\u1EC7n t\xEDch
    h\u01A1n 8.555km vu\xF4ng\r                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
    v\xE0 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 h\u01A1n 2,24 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. \u0110\u01A1n
    v\u1ECB m\u1EDBi t\u1EADp trung ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n h\u1EA1 t\u1EA7ng c\u1EA3ng
    bi\u1EC3n (V\xE2n Phong, Cam Ranh), n\u0103ng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng, du l\u1ECBch,
    b\u1ED9 m\xE1y tinh g\u1ECDn (gi\u1EA3m 129 \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB c\u1EA5p x\xE3)."
